thread.title: Ausy reports H1 net income group share at 4.9 million euros
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Ausy reports H1 net income group share at 4.9 million euros | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Ausy reports H1 net income group share at 4.9 million euros
text:
Sept 16 Ausy SA :
* H1 current operating income 13.9 million euros ($15.68 million) versus 10.4 million euros year ago
* H1 net income group share 4.9 million euros versus 5.0 million euros year ago
* H1 revenue of 191.2 million euros versus 158.5 million euros a year ago Source text for Eikon: ($1 = 0.8864 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
